ssion by worshipping Christ, living in community, getting trained for ministry and making disciples together over time. We ask our partners to uphold some key commitments with this mission in mind and to actively be the church for their city.</p>\r\n    <h2 class=\"nomar blue\">How Do I Become A Partner?</h2>\r\n    <p>Partnership classes are held regularly throughout the year. If you\'d like to receive information about upcoming partnership classes, please sign up here.</p>\r\n    <h2 class=\"nomar blue\">Partnership Commitments</h2>\r\n    <p>Short intro text explaining how Partnership at The Stone takes commitment and what all that means and ya-da-ya-da-ya-da.</p>\r\n    <div class=\"hot_threecol\">\r\n        <h2>Our Partnership Commitments</h2>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"threecol\">\r\n    <div class=\"partner_class\">\r\n        <h2 class=\"blue\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Next Partnership Class</h2>\r\n        <!--<div class=\"rule_partner\"></div>-->\r\n        <h2 class=\"jumbo\">06</h2>\r\n        <h3 class=\"month_partner\">September</h3>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"hot_threecol\" style=\"margin-top: 30px;\">\r\n        <h2>Sign Up For The Class</h2>\r\n    </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"onecol\">\r\n    <div class=\"rule_wh\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"threecol\">\r\n    <h2 class=\"nomar blue\">Partnership Resources</h2>\r\n    <p>Short introduction statement about something resource related that takes up this space here. yep.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"threecol\">\r\n    <h3 class=\"nomar blue\">Missional Communities</h3>\r\n    <p class=\"nomar\">We ask every partner to participate in missional community with The Austin Stone. Find out more about Missional Community.</p>\r\n    <div class=\"rule_wh_short\"></div>\r\n    <h3 class=\"nomar blue\">Affirmation of Faith</h3>\r\n    <p>We ask every partner to participate in missional community with The Austin Stone. Find out more about Missional Community.</p>\r\n    <div c