 church\'s finance team and helped oversee the collection of our tithes/offerings. I continually pray for humility- knowing that only through the power of the Holy Spirit and Christ in me can I glorify God in my marriage, my family, my workplace, and in our church.]]></value>\n</textarea>\n<text identifier=\"919e8599-c2fe-46ae-b177-78dcef40d77b\">\n  <value><![CDATA[Julie]]></value>\n</text>\n<text identifier=\"278956b7-de5e-4111-af94-ae1c0daa398d\">\n  <value><![CDATA[Noah and Hunter]]></value>\n</text>\n<textarea identifier=\"d7c483ed-b6d6-466d-b389-29dfbaa7f576\">\n  <value/>\n</textarea>\n<textarea identifier=\"1147fade-a7be-4b44-9ad8-9a13ed72719b\">\n  <value/>\n</textarea>\n<text identifier=\"7eec99e3-ee9a-4b82-b1ee-4e05dfc7867d\">\n  <value/>\n</text>\n<textarea identifier=\"5a59bbfe-85e9-48fa-b1b0-d6993d37b0b5\">\n  <value/>\n</textarea>\n<text identifier=\"177432fb-2eee-4de4-90a2-651f836db098\">\n  <value/>\n</text>\n<textarea identifier=\"b0c9f815-5b83-494e-8d70-f9b040399363\">\n  <value/>\n</textarea>\n<text identifier=\"07692c1d-064d-40ba-8bb6-3cf30f7dbc14\">\n  <value/>\n</text>\n<textarea identifier=\"609ac5f6-9032-4311-ad25-f0663a4a0901\">\n  <value/>\n</textarea>\n</elements>','{\"metadata.description\":\"\",\"metadata.keywords\":\"\",\"metadata.robots\":\"\",\"metadata.author\":\"\",\"config.enable_comments\":\"0\",\"config.primary_category\":\"110\"}'),(57,8,'person-staff','Devin Garza','devin-garza','2011-08-15 15:41:48','2011-08-15 20:55:23',42,'2011-08-15 15:41:48','0000-00-00 00:00:00',0,0,1,1,42,'',1,'<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"utf-8\"?>\n<elements>\n<image identifier=\"f98a46e7-a524-486d-854a-0078982e5b19\">\n  <file/>\n  <title/>\n  <link/>\n  <target/>\n  <rel/>\n  <lightbox_image/>\n</image>\n<text identifier=\"43963ca5-a280-4737-bdac-a0e0689e940f\">\n  <value/>\n</text>\n<email identifier=\"93bfa239-7873-4a1a-a160-322218b56a12\">\n  <value><![CDATA[dgarza@rwgdocs.com]]></value>\n  <text/>\n  <subject/>\n  <body/>\n</email>\n<text identifier=\"765421ed-4434-4a54-8bde-639b64311d77\">\n  <value/>\n</text>\n<textarea identifier=\"4b686386-9863-4505-9f5c-63b779a04e7e\">\n  <value><![CDATA[Jesus saved me from a self-centered, complacent, worldly existence of shallow faith, and saved me into a relationship that changed the center of my universe and changed the point of reference from which my motivation and identity is derived. <br /><br />My wife Catherine and I have been married 22 years. We have been blessed with four truly amazing kids – Devin Ross, Logan, Meagan, and Graceyn. I have been in practice as an Ob/Gyn in Austin for 17 years and am currently with Renaissance Women’s Group. <br /><br />The Austin Stone has been our church home since 2004. I am currently involved with our partnership in N. Africa and with small group coaching. The power to change hearts is God’s, and evidence of that is seen here at The Austin Stone over and over again, because we exist for the supremacy of the name and purpose of Jesus Christ!]]></value>\n</textarea>\n<text identifier=\"919e8599-c2fe-46ae-b177-78dcef40d77b\">\n  <value><![CDATA[Catherine]]></value>\n</text>\n<text identifier=\"278956b7-de5e-4111-af94-ae1c0daa398d\">\n  <value><![CDATA[Devin Ross, Logan, Meagan, and Graceyn]]></value>\n</text>\n<textarea identifier=\"d7c483ed-b6d6-466d-b389-29dfbaa7f576\">\n  <value/>\n</textarea>\n<textarea identifier=\"1147fade-a7be-4b44-9ad8-9a13ed72719b\">\n  <value/>\n</textarea>\n<text identifier=\"7eec99e3-ee9a-4b82-b1ee-4e05dfc7867d\">\n  <value/>\n</text>\n<textarea identifier=\"5a59bbfe-85e9-48fa-b1b0-d6993d37b0b5\">\n  <value/>\n</textarea>\n<text identifier=\"177432fb-2eee-4de4-90a2-651f836db098\">\n  <value/>\n</text>\n<textarea identifier=\"b0c9f815-5b83-494e-8d70-f9b040399363\">\n  <value/>\n</textarea>\n<text identifier=\"07692c1d-064d-40ba-8bb6-3cf30f7dbc14\">\n  <value/>\n</text>\n<textarea identifier=\"609ac5f6-9032-4311-ad25-f0663a4a0901\">\n  <value/>\n</textarea>\n</elements>','{\"metadata.description\":\"\",\"metadata.keywords\":\"\",\"metadata.robots\":\"\",\"metadata.author\":\"\",\"config.enable_comments\":\"0\",\"config.primary_category\":\"110\"}'),(58,8,'person-staff','Dave Kloubec','dave-kloubec','2011-08-15 15:42:55','2011-08-15 20:55:32',42,'2011-08-15 15:42:55','0000-00-00 00:00:00',0,0,1,1,42,'',1,'<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"utf-8\"?>\n<elements>\n<image identifier=\"f98a46e7-a524-486d-854a-0078982e5b19\">\n  <file/>\n  <title/>\n  <link/>\n  <target/>\n  <rel/>\n  <lightbox_image/>\n</image>\n<text identifier=\"43963ca5-a280-4737-bdac-a0e0689e940f\">\n  <value/>\n</text>\n<email identifier=\"93bfa239-7873-4a1a-a160-322218b56a12\">\n  <value><![CDATA[dave@dmginc.net]]></value>\n  <text/>\n  <subject/>\n  <body/>\n</email>\n<text identifier=\"765421ed-4434-4a54-8bde-639b64311d77\">\n  <value/>\n</text>\n<textarea identifier=\"4b686386-9863-4505-9f5c-63b779a04e7e\">\n  <value><![CDATA[My wife Jenn and I have lived in Austin for 15 years and have been going to The Austin Stone for 6 years. We have two boys, Caleb and Luke, and reside in Round Rock. My wife and I currently serve in the premarital/newlywed and marriage ministries and before that were community group leaders. <br /><br />I graduated from The University of Texas at Austin with a BS in Architectural Engineering. My occupation of 12 years is as a Construction Manager/General Contractor. I balance my work hours with much rest in leisure with family and friends, especially when you add a little BBQ, music, or watching sports. <br /><br />Though my life did not follow a Sunday school example to a tee, I\'ve felt God’s presence and calling in my life as far back as I can remember.&nbsp; Life for me has been a process filled with imperfections yet also with great teachers and the Word itself, and hopefully I\'ll continue to be matured and used for God’s good will. My desire is for God to be glorified in the highest all around me, and for Jesus the Christ to be the primary satisfying value in my life and all peoples’ lives.]]></value>\n</textarea>\n<text identifier=\"919e8599-c2fe-46ae-b177-78dcef40d77b\">\n  <value><![CDATA[Jenn]]></value>\n</text>\n<text identifier=\"278956b7-de5e-4111-af94-ae1c0daa398d\">\n  <value><![CDATA[Caleb and Luke]]></value>\n</text>\n<textarea identifier=\"d7c483ed-b6d6-466d-b389-29dfbaa7f576\">\n  <value/>\n</textarea>\n<textarea identifier=\"1147fade-a7be-4b44-9ad8-9a13ed72719b\">\n  <value/>\n</textarea>\n<text identifier=\"7eec99e3-ee9a-4b82-b1ee-4e05dfc7867d\">\n  <value/>\n</text>\n<textarea identifier=\"5a59bbfe-85e9-48fa-b1b0-d6993d37b0b5\">\n  <value/>\n</textarea>\n<text identifier=\"177432fb-2eee-4de4-90a2-651f836db098\">\n  <value/>\n</text>\n<textarea identifier=\"b0c9f815-5b83-494e-8d70-f9b040399363\">\n  <value/>\n</textarea>\n<text identifier=\"07692c1d-064d-40ba-8bb6-3cf30f7dbc14\">\n  <value/>\n</text>\n<textarea identifier=\"609ac5f6-9032-4311-ad25-f0663a4a0901\">\n  <value/>\n</textarea>\n</elements>','{\"metadata.description\":\"\",\"metadata.keywords\":\"\",\"metadata.robots\":\"\",\"metadata.author\":\"\",\"config.enable_comments\":\"0\",\"config.primary_category\":\"110\"}'),(59,8,'person-staff','Corey Wagner','corey-wagner','2011-08-15 15:44:15','2011-08-15 20:55:42',42,'2011-08-15 15:44:15','0000-00-00 00:00:00',0,0,1,1,42,'',1,'<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"utf-8\"?>\n<elements>\n<image identifier=\"f98a46e7-a524-486d-854a-0078982e5b19\">\n  <file/>\n  <title/>\n  <link/>\n  <target/>\n  <rel/>\n  <lightbox_image/>\n</image>\n<text identifier=\"43963ca5-a280-4737-bdac-a0e0689e940f\">\n  <value/>\n</text>\n<email identifier=\"93bfa239-7873-4a1a-a160-322218b56a12\">\n  <value><![CDATA[cwag15@yahoo.com]]></value>\n  <text/>\n  <subject/>\n  <body/>\n</email>\n<text identifier=\"765421ed-4434-4a54-8bde-639b64311d77\">\n  <value/>\n</text>\n<textarea identifier=\"4b686386-9863-4505-9f5c-63b779a04e7e\">\n  <value><![CDATA[I fell in love with Jesus in college. One night after a Christian event in San Angelo, Texas, God came to me and introduced me to real faith. Before that I lived a life devoted to looking good for people by staying out of trouble and doing the right things. I thought that was what it meant to be a Christian, and it seemed to be the best way to get what I wanted in life. Since college, I have come to realize that following Christ in faith means trusting Him right now and for my future. My walk with Jesus has grown over the years as I have seen His faithfulness to his call over and over again. <br /><br />God put me together with my wife, Brooke, in 2001 while I was still in San Angelo. We lived in Dallas for a couple of years after that, before moving to Austin in 2004. We became partners with The Austin Stone shortly after in 2004. We now have two children, Luke and Carly Kate. <br /><br />Professionally, I recently stepped away from a&nbsp; career as an actuary to follow a call to create a magazine designed to encourage the local church in Austin with stories of what God is doing around town. This has been quite an adventure in faith for a guy who graduated with a math degree! Sounds crazy sometimes, but so does building an ark, I guess. You hear the voice of Jesus, you believe him and you do what He says. You trust Him with everything and find out what He’s doing later.<br /><br />My involvement in ministry here at The Austin Stone has been in marriage counseling and missional community, along with helping to coordinate offering volunteers each month. My vision for the church is for our grandchildren to exist “for the supremacy of the name and purpose of Jesus Christ”, holding fast to the word of God and sound doctrine and teaching their children to carry on in it as well.]]></value>\n</textarea>\n<text identifier=\"919e8599-c2fe-46ae-b177-78dcef40d77b\">\n  <value><![CDATA[Brooke]]></value>\n</text>\n<text identifier=\"278956b7-de5e-4111-af94-ae1c0daa398d\">\n  <value><![CDATA[Luke and Carly Kate]]></value>\n</text>\n<textarea identifier=\"d7c483ed-b6d6-466d-b389-29dfbaa7f576\">\n  <value/>\n</textarea>\n<textarea identifier=\"1147fade-a7be-4b44-9ad8-9a13ed72719b\">\n  <value/>\n</textarea>\n<text identifier=\"7eec99e3-ee9a-4b82-b1ee-4e05dfc7867d\">\n  <value/>\n</text>\n<textarea identifier=\"5a59bbfe-85e9-48fa-b1b0-d6993d37b0b5\">\n  <value/>\n</textarea>\n<text identifier=\"177432fb-2eee-4de4-90a2-651f836db098\">\n  <value/>\n</text>\n<textarea identifier=\"b0c9f815-5b83-494e-8d70-f9b040399363\">\n  <value/>\n</textarea>\n<text identifier=\"07692c1d-064d-40ba-8bb6-3cf30f7dbc14\">\n  <value/>\n</text>\n<textarea identifier=\"609ac5f6-9032-4311-ad25-f0663a4a0901\">\n  <value/>\n</textarea>\n</elements>','{\"metadata.description\":\"\",\"metadata.keywords\":\"\",\"metadata.robots\":\"\",\"metadata.author\":\"\",\"config.enable_comments\":\"0\",\"config.primary_category\":\"110\"}'),(60,8,'person-staff','Brian Riley','brian-riley','2011-08-15 15:45:23','2011-08-15 20:55:50',42,'2011-08-15 15:45:23','0000-00-00 00:00:00',0,0,1,1,42,'',1,'<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"utf-8\"?>\n<elements>\n<image identifier=\"f98a46e7-a524-486d-854a-0078982e5b19\">\n  <file/>\n  <title/>\n  <link/>\n  <target/>\n  <rel/>\n  <lightbox_image/>\n</image>\n<text identifier=\"43963ca5-a280-4737-bdac-a0e0689e940f\">\n  <value/>\n</text>\n<email identifier=\"93bfa239-7873-4a1a-a160-322218b56a12\">\n  <value><![CDATA[brian@rgsearch.com]]></value>\n  <text/>\n  <subject/>\n  <body/>\n</email>\n<text identifier=\"765421ed-4434-4a54-8bde-639b64311d77\">\n  <value/>\n</text>\n<textarea identifier=\"4b686386-9863-4505-9f5c-63b779a04e7e\">\n  <value><![CDATA[Jesus transformed my life 17 years ago, when my selfishness and need for approval were exposed in such a way that my only hope was the saving grace of Jesus Christ. It is only through the power of the Holy Spirit, that He continues to refine me and propel me to serve others in His Name. <br /><br />My wife Karen and I serve the body of The Austin Stone in leading the pre-marital mentoring ministry. Our passion is to share with couples that their marriage depends on the Gospel and our vision is to see their marriages display and proclaim Christ to others.<br /><br />We have three children and live in Central Austin. I graduated from The University of Texas and for work, own a recruiting firm, RG Search, that specializes in executive search.]]></value>\n</textarea>\n<text identifier=\"919e8599-c2fe-46ae-b177-78dcef40d77b\">\n  <value><![CDATA[Karen]]></value>\n</text>\n<text identifier=\"278956b7-de5e-4111-af94-ae1c0daa398d\">\n  <value><![CDATA[Ian, Grace, and Paige]]></value>\n</text>\n<textarea identifier=\"d7c483ed-b6d6-466d-b389-29dfbaa7f576\">\n  <value/>\n</textarea>\n<textarea identifier=\"1147fade-a7be-4b44-9ad8-9a13ed72719b\">\n  <value/>\n</textarea>\n<text identifier=\"7eec99e3-ee9a-4b82-b1ee-4e05dfc7867d\">\n  <value/>\n</text>\n<textarea identifier=\"5a59bbfe-85e9-48fa-b1b0-d6993d37b0b5\">\n  <value/>\n</textarea>\n<text identifier=\"177432fb-2eee-4de4-90a2-651f836db098\">\n  <value/>\n</text>\n<textarea identifier=\"b0c9f815-5b83-494e-8d70-f9b040399363\">\n  <value/>\n</textarea>\n<text identifier=\"07692c1d-064d-40ba-8bb6-3cf30f7dbc14\">\n  <value/>\n</text>\n<textarea identifier=\"609ac5f6-9032-4311-ad25-f0663a4a0901\">\n  <value/>\n</textarea>\n</elements>','{\"metadata.description\":\"\",\"metadata.keywords\":\"\",\"metadata.robots\":\"\",\"metadata.author\":\"\",\"config.enable_comments\":\"0\",\"config.primary_category\":\"110\"}'),(61,8,'person-staff','D Thompson','d-thompson','2011-08-15 15:46:28','2011-08-15 15:48:01',42,'2011-08-15 15:46:28','0000-00-00 00:00:00',0,1,1,1,42,'',1,'<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"utf-8\"?>\n<elements>\n<image identifier=\"f98a46e7-a524-486d-854a-0078982e5b19\">\n  <file/>\n  <title/>\n  <link/>\n  <target/>\n  <rel/>\n  <lightbox_image/>\n</image>\n<text identifier=\"43963ca5-a280-4737-bdac-a0e0689e940f\">\n  <value><![CDATA[Pastoral Ministry Assistant to Matt Carter]]></value>\n</