p;<br />Today, I serve The Austin Stone in the areas of preaching, pastoral counseling, and missional community leadership. Christy and I have been blessed with two great kids - Paige and Tyler.]]></value>\n</textarea>\n<text identifier=\"919e8599-c2fe-46ae-b177-78dcef40d77b\">\n  <value><![CDATA[Christy]]></value>\n</text>\n<text identifier=\"278956b7-de5e-4111-af94-ae1c0daa398d\">\n  <value><![CDATA[Paige and Tyler]]></value>\n</text>\n<textarea identifier=\"d7c483ed-b6d6-466d-b389-29dfbaa7f576\">\n  <value/>\n</textarea>\n<text identifier=\"f3ab1beb-7fb8-4b43-b1ae-4300f96baf52\">\n  <value/>\n</text>\n<text identifier=\"7eec99e3-ee9a-4b82-b1ee-4e05dfc7867d\">\n  <value/>\n</text>\n</elements>','{\"metadata.description\":\"\",\"metadata.keywords\":\"\",\"metadata.robots\":\"\",\"metadata.author\":\"\",\"config.enable_comments\":\"0\",\"config.primary_category\":\"110\"}'),(68,8,'person-staff','Beth Murray','beth-murray','2011-08-15 15:56:52','2011-08-15 15:57:46',42,'2011-08-15 15:56:52','0000-00-00 00:00:00',0,0,1,1,42,'',1,'<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"utf-8\"?>\n<elements>\n<image identifier=\"f98a46e7-a524-486d-854a-0078982e5b19\">\n  <file/>\n  <title/>\n  <link/>\n  <target/>\n  <rel/>\n  <lightbox_image/>\n</image>\n<text identifier=\"43963ca5-a280-4737-bdac-a0e0689e940f\">\n  <value><![CDATA[Connections Associate]]></value>\n</text>\n<email identifier=\"93bfa239-7873-4a1a-a160-322218b56a12\">\n  <value><![CDATA[beth@austinstone.org]]></value>\n  <text/>\n  <subject/>\n  <body/>\n</email>\n<text identifier=\"765421ed-4434-4a54-8bde-639b64311d77\">\n  <value><![CDATA[bethlee]]></value>\n</text>\n<textarea identifier=\"4b686386-9863-4505-9f5c-63b779a04e7e\">\n  <value/>\n</textarea>\n<text identifier=\"919e8599-c2fe-46ae-b177-78dcef40d77b\">\n  <value/>\n</text>\n<text identifier=\"278956b7-de5e-4111-af94-ae1c0daa398d\">\n  <value/>\n</text>\n<textarea identifier=\"d7c483ed-b6d6-466d-b389-29dfbaa7f576\">\n  <value/>\n</textarea>\n<text identifier=\"f3ab1b